history.content: Your EGT is still Summer 2022, but you can still walk in the Spring

Hello!

I am filling out the expected graduation term change request form and wanted to make sure that i am doing it correctly. 

My original graduation date is spring 2023 but i am trying to complete my undergrad this spring 2022. I plan on taking one more class during summer to finish off, so would my grad date be spring 2022 or summer 2022?

I talked to a couselor and she stated that i could walk the stage w one class left that i can take during summer but idk if that would mean my grad date is spring 2022 or summer 2022? 

If anyone could clarify, that would be great!

https://lsadvising.berkeley.edu/sites/default/files/expectedgraduationtermchangerequest_fillable2.pdf
